#

Southwest Burger

25 min
$12.5
650 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinGluten Friendly

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

QuickDeliciousGrill

Description

A zesty burger topped with spicy chipotle sauce, fresh avocado, and pepper jack cheese for a flavor-packed bite.

Ingredients

  • ground beef: 1 pound
  • burger buns: 4
  • pepper jack cheese slices: 4
  • avocado: 1, sliced
  • chipotle sauce: 1/4 cup
  • lettuce: 1 cup, shredded
  • tomato: 1, sliced
  • onion: 1, sliced
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
